Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "lili" in different forms and positions:

1. *Lili* je danas donela predivan buket cveća. (Lili brought a beautiful bouquet of flowers today.)
2. Videla sam kako *lili* raste u vrtu. (I saw how the lily was growing in the garden.)
3. *Liliju* treba zalivati svaka tri dana. (The lily needs to be watered every three days.)
4. Na slici je prelepa *lila* boja. (The picture shows a beautiful lilac color.)
5. Da li znaš gde mogu da kupim *lile*? (Do you know where I can buy lilies?)
6. Moj omiljeni parfem ima miris *lilija*. (My favorite perfume has the scent of lilies.)
7. *Lilica* je mala i slatka. (Lilica is small and cute.)
8. Sinoć sam sanjala veliku *lilu*. (Last night I dreamed of a big lily.)

I hope this helps!